      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Siding with TERILEE (5) who resumed off a short break at Pakenham over this trip and ran a strong race behind Paradise City, who won a Group race at Flemington next time out. She looks to get in very well at the weights here with 55.5kg after the claim and sets up nicely from the gate. ALL BUSINESS (4) was a good winner two back at Geelong, close up in third last time behind Mystery 'N' Drama who has since placed in Group company at Caulfield. She'll be very hard to hold out. BRUTALINA (6) hasn't fired in three runs this time in over shorter but can do much better out to 1400m having shown ability up to this level last time in work. FLOWERDALE (7) resumed with a tidy win at Sale in easier and looks progressive enough to measure up to this. TRIAL BY PRESS (3) was solid fresh and has each-way claims.",
